{"tid":1806037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[超越香港] 不少澳門輕軌乘客 2020年0:00後不能出閘","createTime":"2020-01-01T04:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T05:11:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"108b3e77822f595d3ecb08a94eae0e0486ed2d93","tid":1806037,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"昨晚是輕軌通車後首個除夕，為方便市民外出參與倒數活動，氹仔線亦特別延長服務時間，吸引不少市民乘搭。<br />\n<br />\n不過，踏入 2020 年，各站閘機口開始出現乘客未能出閘情況，據了解，不少乘客於 2019 年正常入閘，但在 00:00 後均出閘失敗，閘機顯示「車票無效」訊息，由於受阻乘客越來越多影響車站運作，職員直接打開閘機，乘客無須使用車票可以直接進出車站。<br />\n<br />\n有職員透露，故障或可能涉及車票系統的時間設定，但具體詳情則不得而知。"},{"pid":"d6c10d5170348094dd5a4b50d2bce4c230c9822a","tid":1806037,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"元旦大遊行和理非手足必加技能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區&nbsp;"},{"pid":"b84972a3c31cc92234d1005cffebdfa6d7f95ea0","tid":1806037,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"千年蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e134cdf1617c3864b921a299778627cbe7b1f26e","tid":1806037,"uid":69841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"2020年都仲有十年蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe41f24af6f54be38a4714c6cbbee90996319c7","tid":1806037,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8305be815a30fbf604ccbeac51e8eaa18a9b55c","tid":1806037,"uid":134415,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"